ly-Eulerian interface-driven adaptive\nFSI model to simulate the contact and bouncing phenomenon between an elastic\nsolid and a rigid wall.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Dec 2021 05:25:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2022 02:05:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 6 Feb 2022 17:17:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-08"}
