tion pattern. BTS shows 5,556x and 1,306x improved\nexecution time on ResNet-20 and logistic regression over a CPU, with a chip\narea of 373.6mm^2 and up to 163.2W of power.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Dec 2021 14:34:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2022 02:42:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-02"}
